  "contents": "<article>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 class=\"no-toc\" id=\"async\"><a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/testing/async#async\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a>async</h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label function\">function</label>\n    \n    \n    \n    <span class=\"version\"></span>\n  </header>\n\n  \n  <!-- INFO BAR -->\n<section class=\"info-bar\">\n\n<table class=\"is-full-width\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n  <th>npm Package</th>\n  <td><a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/@angular/core\">@angular/core</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <th>Module</th>\n  <td><code>import { <a href=\"api/core/testing/async\" class=\"code-anchor\">async</a> } from <a href=\"api/core/testing\">'@angular/core/testing'</a>;</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <th>Source</th>\n  <td><a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/5.2.11/packages/core/testing/src/async.ts#L12-L60\">core/testing/src/async.ts</a></td>\n</tr>\n\n</tbody>\n</table>\n\n  \n  \n  \n  \n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">\nfunction <a href=\"api/core/testing/async\" class=\"code-anchor\">async</a>(fn: Function): (done: any) => any;\n</code-example>\n\n  \n\n  \n\n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\"><a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/testing/async#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a>Description</h2>\n  <p>Wraps a test function in an asynchronous test zone. The test will automatically\ncomplete when all asynchronous calls within this zone are done. Can be used\nto wrap an <a href=\"api/core/testing/inject\"><code>inject</code></a> call.</p>\n<p>Example:</p>\n<code-example>\nit('...', <a href=\"api/core/testing/async\" class=\"code-anchor\">async</a>(<a href=\"api/core/testing/inject\" class=\"code-anchor\">inject</a>([AClass], (object) => {\n  object.doSomething.then(() => {\n    expect(...);\n  })\n});\n</code-example>\n\n</section>\n\n\n\n\n\n</section></article>\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/common/AsyncPipe\n - api/common/NgIf\n - api/core/testing\n - api/core/testing/fakeAsync\n - api/core/testing/inject\n - api/core/testing/tick\n - api/http/testing/MockBackend\n - guide/http\n - guide/pipes\n - guide/reactive-forms\n - guide/router\n - guide/rx-library\n - guide/testing\n - guide/upgrade\n - tutorial/toh-pt6\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - api/core/testing\n - api/core/testing/async#async\n - api/core/testing/async#description\n - api/core/testing/inject\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/5.2.11/packages/core/testing/src/async.ts#L12-L60\n - https://www.npmjs.com/package/@angular/core\n-->"
